      <title>拜耳因作物产量表现不佳下调盈利预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/bayer-lower-earnings-guidance-on-weak-crop-unit-performance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于备受争议的除草剂 Roundup 等农产品价格持续低迷，拜耳公司下调了今年的利润预期，并表示明年的收益可能会下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/bayer-lower-earnings-guidance-on-weak-crop-unit-performance</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 06:53:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划和刺激计划失败导致中国股市和人民币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/chinese-stocks-fall-as-trump-s-cabinet-picks-hurt-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一系列令人失望的经济发展形势下，对中美紧张局势恶化的担忧进一步削弱了投资者信心，导致中国股市和人民币暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/chinese-stocks-fall-as-trump-s-cabinet-picks-hurt-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 06:10:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
